wiki.summary: "Panda" is the commercial debut single by American rapper Desiigner. The song premiered on December 15, 2015, and was released for digital download on the iTunes Store as a single on December 20, 2015, before being re-released on February 26, 2016. The song was written by Desiigner and its producer Menace. "Panda" was heavily sampled by Designer's fellow GOOD Music label-mate and founder Kanye West, for "Pt. 2", a song on West's seventh studio album The Life of Pablo, and inspired a number of remixes. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: "Panda" is the commercial debut single by American rapper Desiigner. The song premiered on December 15, 2015, and was released for digital download on the iTunes Store as a single on December 20, 2015, before being re-released on February 26, 2016. The song was written by Desiigner and its producer Menace. "Panda" was heavily sampled by Designer's fellow GOOD Music label-mate and founder Kanye West, for "Pt. 2", a song on West's seventh studio album The Life of Pablo, and inspired a number of remixes. The single topped the US Billboard Hot 100 for two consecutive weeks. An official video was released on 10 May 2016, exclusively through Tidal. Read more on Last.fm.
